videos.headline: Pitt QB floors it for 30-yard TD run
videos.description: Pittsburgh QB Kenny Pickett keeps the triple-option read and jets into the end zone untouched for a 30-yard touchdown sprint.

videos.headline: Duke QB dives to score on 6-yard keeper
videos.description: Quentin Harris fakes the pitch, storms through a hole, and dives into the end zone for a 6-yard Duke touchdown to knot the score at 7.

videos.headline: Duke QB lofts beautiful 3-yard fade TD
videos.description: Duke QB Daniel Jones rainbows a pretty fade to T.J. Rahming, who slides and hauls in the 3-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Jones, Rahming connect again for 4-yard TD
videos.description: Daniel Jones whips a quick strike to T.J. Rahming for a 4-yard Duke touchdown, their second scoring connection of the game.

videos.headline: Pickett rips perfect 50-yard TD heave
videos.description: Pittsburgh carves into Duke's lead as QB Kenny Pickett hurls a beautiful 50-yard touchdown to Maurice Ffrench.

videos.headline: Jones hits Jackson for 74-yard catch-and-run
videos.description: Daniel Jones threads the needle to Deon Jackson on the sideline, who sheds a tackle and breaks free for a 74-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Carter zooms in 31-yard TD
videos.description: V'Lique Carter secures the carry in motion and zips into the end zone for a 31-yard Pittsburgh touchdown.

videos.headline: Duke WR breaks off 68-yard TD catch
videos.description: Daniel Jones throws a strike to Johnathan Lloyd, who weaves through traffic and shows off his speed for a 68-yard touchdown.
